Package grafioschtrader.entities.projection

Interface SecurityYearClose

public interface SecurityYearClose
Projection interface representing annual summary data for a security, including the year-end close price, total dividends for the year, and an optional currency pair close for conversion.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    double
    getCurrencyClose()
    The closing price of the associated currency pair on the year-end date, used for currency conversion of the security close and dividends.
    LocalDate
    getDate()
    The date of the year-end record (typically December 31 of the year).
    double
    getSecurityClose()
    The security’s closing price on the year-end date.
    double
    getYearDiv()
    The total sum of dividends paid by the security during the year.
